dataset_id: TOMS Nimbus-7 Total Column Ozone Daily and Monthly Zonal Means V008 (TOMSN7L3ztoz) at GES DISC
title: TOMS Nimbus-7 Total Column Ozone Daily and Monthly Zonal Means V008 (TOMSN7L3ztoz) at GES DISC
summary:
This Nimbus-7 Total Ozone Mapping Spectrometer (TOMS) version 8 daily zonal means data product contains total column ozone values. The data are averaged in 5 degree latitude bands. These data are stored in an ASCII format.

The TOMS data were produced by the Laboratory for Atmospheres at NASA Goddard Space Flight Center (Code 614).
